# Keeps resources/ocr/ present so the desktop bundler (tauri.conf.json
# bundle.resources) always has a source dir, even on a clean checkout —
# tauri-build hard-errors on a missing resource path, which broke every
# fresh-checkout desktop build between 0.10.0 and this fix.
# npm run fetch:model fills it with the OCR detection/recognition models
# (gitignored).
